+| File | Description |
+|------|-------------|
+| `include/ut0core.h` | `ut::Location` struct for source location tracking |
+| `include/ut0cpu_cache.h` | `Cacheline_padded` template for cache line padding |
+| `include/ut0class_life_cycle.h` | `Non_copyable` base class for RAII guards |
+| `include/sync0sharded_rw.h` | `Sharded_rw_lock` class for scalable read-write locking |
+| `include/lock0latches.h` | `locksys::Latches` class with Page_shards and Table_shards |
+| `include/lock0guards.h` | RAII guard classes for latch management |
+
