+- `LOCK_SYS_GLOBAL` with `SYNC_LOCK_SYS_GLOBAL` level
+- `LOCK_SYS_PAGE` with `SYNC_LOCK_SYS_SHARDED` level
+- `LOCK_SYS_TABLE` with `SYNC_LOCK_SYS_SHARDED` level
+
